  <custodhist id="aspace_a0b015f5370446476f7dbd955cf0e8cb">
    <head>Provenance</head>
<p>The George Marion Papers were donated to the Abraham Lincoln Brigade Archives collections in October, 1983 by Elizabeth Craney Marion, George Marion's second wife. This collection came to New York University in January 2001 as part of the original acquisition of ALBA collections, formerly housed at Brandeis University.</p>  </custodhist>
